File->Save

"Save" is used to save all your work. It saves the entire scene
(including objects, lights, environment, etc) on the main scene file
in the scene folder of the project.  To save off selected objects onto
separate files, use Sculptor->Save.

You can also turn on the auto-save option to make a backup at regular
intervals (see Settings->Project Settings). Note that the backup file
is different from the original , and is used while restarting the
program after an abnormal exit (what's that?!). So it is recommended
that you use "Save" frequently, to make your changes permanent.
